      "comment": "MUSCLEM (5) comes through the Nutrien Classic Sales series at Wagga where she was fourth on debut in the heats then improved to place in the final at Listed level. On the up and will enjoy the drop in class to maiden grade. THE WOOL BROKER (4) made an encouraging debut when he finished 2.5 metres from the winner in second at Maryborough. Same draw and with natural improvement likely he could go one better. KYVALLEY DIABLO (3) is a gelding by Classic Connection on debut for the Chris Svanosio yard. Has been trialling well, winning his latest hitout at Melton. Anticipating a bright start to his career. ROCKINWITHSASS (8) is a filly by Aldebaran Eagle on debut. Won her latest trial here and there is no harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon.",
